					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">The standalone convergence test turned out to be 1.25 KiB, but iNES format rounds that up to 16 KiB.<br /><br />Left: Switch to grid (or toggle center dot)<br />Right: Switch to solid color (or toggle white/red)<br />Start: Toggle help<br /><br />Automatically detects PAL or NTSC, using 7x8 pixel cells on NTSC or 8x11 pixel cells on PAL.</div>

					
